high_descs: Move to the sink, forward and to the right.
Pick up the potato in the sink.
Turn around, go to the table with the potato, turn left, go to the microwave to the table in the corner to the right.
Heat the potato in the microwave.
Bring the heated potato back across the room to the opposite corner, to the small black table left of the sink.
Put the heated potato on the small black table.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated potato on the small black table.

high_descs: Move to your right facing the sink
Pick up the potato in the sink
Turn right then head to the microwave
Open the microwave put in and out the potato then close the microwave
Turn left walk forward head towards the island on the left side of the sink counter
Put the potato on the edge of the island
anns.task_desc: Put the heated potato on the island

high_descs: Turn right and go to the sink.
Pick up the potato in the sink.
Turn around and go forward toward the white table, then turn left and go to the table with the microwave on it.
Open the microwave and cook the potato inside it, then take it out.
Turn left, move forward, then turn left to go to the table across the room, then turn right to face the black table.
Put the potato on the black table.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked potato on the table.
